race.description: First National Bonnici And Associates Mdn Plate
race.comment: SHYAMALAN (2) debuts for the Hayes yard and has looked the goods at the jumpouts. Maps well enough and has the blinkers on, suggesting intent. A bold run is on the cards. Ditto from COSMIC DYNASTY (8), who has also impressed at the jumpouts. McDougall is a positive jockey booking and expect her to go well. DALSICON (6) resumed here improved beaten 3L when expected to need it. Strips fitter and can get into the finish again. VERY TORQUEE (5) also draws awkwardly but is sure to build on his solid Wangaratta placing on debut. SIR FOX (3) finished sixth last start, beaten 5.5 lengths at Wangaratta over 1100m. Value at odds.
